            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> This was already discussed, why do we need a new issue?\n\nBecause I think that issue is not very relevant now. Nvim has already removed `'imcmdline'` and `'imdisable'`, removing `'imsearch'` is not a big deal for me.\n\nAnd I don't think supporting `'imactivatefunc'` and `'imstatusfunc'` have to change the idea of whether to remove `'imdisable'`, `'imcmdline'` and `'imsearch'` (I think `'iminsert' + 'imactivatefunc'` is enough for me).",
